{"arkId":"cl010118096","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010118096","modified ":"2026-03-02","title":"Montre octogonale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre octogonale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1625","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1625,"imprecision":"","text":"1er quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Durant, Pierre","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7044","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Bo\u00eetier octogonale compos\u00e9 de deux couvercles mont\u00e9s \u00e0 charni\u00e8re et d\u0027une carrure. Couvercle du cadran orn\u00e9 au centre d\u0027un m\u00e9daillon octogonal : Lapidation de saint Etienne ; dans les compartiments du pourtour sont grav\u00e9s des fruits, des rinceaux fleuris, deux anges et un coeur ail\u00e9. Couvercle du mouvement offrant un d\u00e9cor similaire, m\u00e9daillon central repr\u00e9sentant Suzanne au bain et les deux vieillards. Charni\u00e8res grav\u00e9es de deux t\u00eates d\u0027angelot ; carrure grav\u00e9e de rinceaux de feuillage. Plaque du cadran grav\u00e9e de rinceaux fleuris o\u00f9 apparaissent une t\u00eate de dauphin et deux enfants couch\u00e9s encadrant deux coeurs ail\u00e9s au-dessus d\u0027une couronne ; au centre de l\u0027anneau horaire rapport\u00e9 figure un paysage avec en arri\u00e8re-plan un village. Echappement \u00e0 verge, fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq rectangulaire et cliquet reperc\u00e9s et grav\u00e9s de fleurs de fraisier m\u00eal\u00e9es \u00e0 des rinceaux.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : P\/Durant\/ARouen","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5","displayDimension":"5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"2,6","displayDimension":"2,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,2","displayDimension":"2,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Rouen (Haute-Normandie = Haute Normandie-\u003ESeine-Maritime = Seine Maritime)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Louis Fould (1794-1858), vente \u00e0 Paris 20 rue de Berry, 4 juin 1860 et jours suivants n\u00b0 2318 ; collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"Fould, Louis","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Louis XIII (1610-1643)"}],"place":[{"value":"Rouen"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horloge